drop table if exists sport_record_of_id;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: sport_record_of_id */
/*==============================================================*/
create table sport_record_of_id
(
itemid int(6) character set utf8 not null auto_increment comment '该记录的号码',
single_score int(6) comment '该次跑操所得分数',
term varchar(20) not null comment '学期',
date date not null comment '日期',
start_time timestamp not null comment '具体开始时间',
end_time timestamp not null comment '结束时间',
area varchar(20) not null comment '跑操地址',
length double(16,3) comment '所跑长度',
steps int(10) comment '步数',
moments varchar(100) comment '实时时间数组',
speed double(16,3) comment '实时速度数组',
calories double(16,3) comment '消耗的总卡路里',
primary key (itemid)
);

alter table sport_record_of_id comment '每个用户有自己的运动记录表';
